TITLE: Basic RQL Query Example
DESCRIPTION: Example of a simple RQL query filtering for foo="ditto" and bar<10 using logical AND operator.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/basic-rql.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: rql
CODE:
```
and(eq(foo,"ditto"),lt(bar,10))
```

