TITLE: Minimal Thing Representation in JSON for Eclipse Ditto API v2
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the most minimalistic representation of a Thing in Eclipse Ditto API version 2. It includes only the required fields: thingId and policyId.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/basic-overview.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "thingId": "the.namespace:the-thing-id",
  "policyId": "the.namespace:the-policy-id"
}
```

