TITLE: Installing Eclipse Ditto using Helm
DESCRIPTION: Command to install the Eclipse Ditto Helm chart from Docker Hub registry with a specific version. The command creates a release named 'my-ditto' in the 'ditto' namespace and waits for the deployment to complete.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/deployment/helm/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
helm install -n ditto my-ditto oci://registry-1.docker.io/eclipse/ditto --version <version> --wait
```

