TITLE: Configuring Declared Acknowledgement Labels in Ditto Connection Source
DESCRIPTION: JSON configuration for declaring allowed acknowledgement labels for a source. This example shows how to declare a custom acknowledgement label using the connection ID placeholder.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/basic-connections.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "addresses": [
    "<source>"
  ],
  "authorizationContext": ["ditto:inbound-auth-subject"],
  "declaredAcks": [
    "{{connection:id}}:my-custom-ack"
  ]
}
```

