LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
curl -u ditto:ditto -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{
   "definition": "https://eclipse-ditto.github.io/ditto-examples/wot/models/floor-lamp-1.0.0.tm.jsonld",
   "attributes": {
     "manufacturer": "ACME",
     "VIN": "0815666337"
   }
 }' 'http://localhost:8080/api/2/things'
```

