TITLE: Querying Things with RQL in Eclipse Ditto
DESCRIPTION: Example of an RQL query to search for things located in the 'living-room', sorted by thing ID, and limited to 5 results.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/basic-search.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: rql
CODE:
```
Filter:     eq(attributes/location,"living-room")
Sorting:    sort(+thingId)
Paging:     size(5),cursor(CURSOR_ID)
```

