SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/connectivity-mapping.md#2025-04-17_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{ 
  "name": "exampleConnection",
  "sources": [{
      "addresses": ["<source>"],
      "authorizationContext": ["ditto:inbound"],
      "payloadMapping": ["Ditto", "status"]
    }
  ],
  "mappingDefinitions": {
    "status": {
      "mappingEngine": "ConnectionStatus",
      "options": {
        "thingId": "{%raw%}{{ header:device_id }}{%endraw%}"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

