TITLE: Configuring Custom Aggregation Metrics in HOCON (New Format for 3.7.3)
DESCRIPTION: Updated configuration format for custom aggregation metrics in Eclipse Ditto 3.7.3. This new format removes the filters object and uses a single filter property for each metric.
