TITLE: RQL Filter Translation Example - Wildcard Feature
DESCRIPTION: Example of translated RQL filter for querying properties across all features with authorization checks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/architecture/DADR-0008-wildcard-search-index.md#2025-04-17_snippet_4

