TITLE: Defining a Policy JSON Object in Eclipse Ditto
DESCRIPTION: This JSON example defines a complete Policy document for an IoT Thing with different access levels. It includes owner permissions with full access, observer permissions with read-only access to specific features, and privacy restrictions to prevent certain users from accessing sensitive data.
