TITLE: Enabling Connection Logs via Piggyback Command
DESCRIPTION: DevOps command for enabling logging for a specific connection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/connectivity-manage-connections-piggyback.md#2025-04-17_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "targetActorSelection": "/system/sharding/connection",
  "headers": {
    "aggregate": false,
    "is-group-topic": false,
    "ditto-sudo": true
  },
  "piggybackCommand": {
    "type": "connectivity.commands:enableConnectionLogs",
    "connectionId": "<connectionID>"
  }
}
```

