TITLE: Complete AMQP 0.9.1 Connection Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Full JSON configuration example for establishing an AMQP 0.9.1 connection including sources and targets.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eclipse-ditto/ditto/blob/master/documentation/src/main/resources/pages/ditto/connectivity-protocol-bindings-amqp091.md#2025-04-17_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "connection": {
    "id": "rabbit-example-connection-123",
    "connectionType": "amqp-091",
    "connectionStatus": "open",
    "failoverEnabled": true,
    "uri": "amqp://user:password@localhost:5672/vhost",
    "sources": [
      {
        "addresses": [
          "queueName"
        ],
        "authorizationContext": ["ditto:inbound-auth-subject", "..."]
      }
    ],
    "targets": [
      {
        "address": "exchangeName/routingKey",
        "topics": [
          "_/_/things/twin/events",
          "_/_/things/live/messages"
        ],
        "authorizationContext": ["ditto:outbound-auth-subject", "..."]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

